                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.248/6–2849: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Taipei</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Krentz</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-06-28T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 28, 1949—5 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>155. Nat Govt querying market substantial quantities avgas for delivery Taiwan.
                    Dept desires your best estimate mil stocks avgas on island and current rate
                        CAF<note n="43" xml:id="d965fn43">Chinese Air Force.</note> consumption.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
